        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Honey-Soy Chicken With Sauce. Built in the way Chinese home kitchens cook: fast at the wok, balance at the bowl. Adjustable for what you need."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A weeknight-friendly recipe: most of the work is the prep, and the cooking takes care of itself."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "What you need"
          }
        ]
